m', 'The use of tetrabenazine in combination with neuroleptic agents or other dopamine antagonists should preferably be avoided.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/170511/', '', 'Dalfampridine, Inotersen, Riluzole, Tafamidis', '', 1767369485);
