ergism', 'The use of tetrabenazine in combination with neuroleptic agents or other dopamine antagonists should preferably be avoided.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/170570/', '', 'Ketotifen, Fexofenadine, Loratadine, Desloratadine, Azelastine', 'Dalfampridine, Riluzole, Inotersen, Pitolisant, Tafamidis', 1767369485);
